data.description: Come see this Gorgeous 4 Bedroom, 3 Bath 2 car garage home that features great open Living area on main level with office or den/ game room and bedroom, The second level has a large loft, Spacious Master suite with 2 additional bedrooms. The gated community has a beautiful Clubhouse, pool, exercise room, tennis, basketball & playground. It's just a short walk to Allapattah Flats K-8 school, Close to shopping and restaurants, you don't want to miss this one!
